<br>
"Hey, I killed xxx mob and lost xxx faction and I cannot complete my epic quest!"<br>
<br>
I mean giving you a spell called scoriae/wildfire allows you to burn everything in your way?  Isn't there at least a little bit of common roleplaying here?  I mean do you really want to go out and torch Kelethin and then come running here to find out uber_01_way_to_fix_your_faction_in_2_seconds00!<br>
<br>
Get a clue.  Don't burn everything that comes across your path because someday, for some odd reason (maybe your epic?), you might have a use for it. <p><font color="#006600"><font size=+2>Quigsby Quickfoot</font></font>
